{"tid":935711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵又縮班？內地網站顯示下月部分來港列車班次勁減一半","createTime":"2018-12-10T08:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T11:59:33.000Z","uid":20058,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"488beb88f1f95daa841ce7488672ad700635800c","tid":935711,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"高鐵香港段自今年9月23日通車以來客量一直未如理想，而自下月起更會調整班次，部分內地南下列車班次每日大減10多班。東網記者查看港鐵高鐵購票網站，及中國鐵路客戶服務中心購票網站「12306」，發現自下月5日起，由廣州南站、深圳北站及福田站開往香港的班次有大幅調整，除了班次減少外，部分路線的首班車及尾班車開出時間亦有改動。<br />\n<br />\n根據港鐵及「12306」網站，由廣州南站開往香港西九龍站的高鐵列車，自1月5日起由每日34班減至每日21班，減少約38%；首班列車開出時間由早上6時48分延遲至8時半，延後近2小時。而由深圳北站開往香港的列車班次，亦由每日65班減至54班。福田站往香港的列車，雖然周末班次未有太大變動，但平日班次由27班減至15班，減少近一半。<br />\n<br />\n至於由香港開往廣州南站及深圳北站的列車，雖然每日班次只是略減數班，但尾班車開出時間提早不少。<span style=\"color: red;\">往廣州南及深圳北的尾班車開出時間由原本的晚上10時50分，提前至晚上8時58分。<br />\n</span><a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181210/bkn-20181210123912435-1210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181210%2Fbkn-20181210123912435-1210_00822_001.html&d=qXvIiLPhcgzIZTgxll1D%2FsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3e7dc4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181210/bkn-20181210123912435-1210_00822_001.html</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815863eaa438cb69121d930d3e116a59e47470ef","tid":935711,"uid":77196,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4Qd837.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4Qd837.png&h=d82e8173&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bb758589518ec668dfbdf202d309cb6af900c42","tid":935711,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"都預料到架，唔係新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68900740627a8eca479476010496a3360603bd7","tid":935711,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"8:50尾班.....方便支那d官落黎叫雞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac74c096cf59678eb08ab2f8a84e29e068f1e80","tid":935711,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91471b330871631e2aa01ca3c295d645f62ed369","tid":935711,"uid":20284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"龜鐵都有新時間表睇, 個表每個方向得番一版半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ffdaf08b80c59fec4c1d1149d83c2b6b81c471","tid":935711,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c47efeafc544e5ee85fe08923efa96f7f682025","tid":935711,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"預咗㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0360bba44509db6264440504ab7d8d035a975b1","tid":935711,"uid":21917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"今次真係搞手無得賺 只求打個和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29872d6bc5d834eef0cb64eac6761b2545b2447f","tid":935711,"uid":55913,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:41:28.000Z","m